                        via Navy channels.</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945Malta</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d196</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">196</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1944-11-18T00:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1944-11-18T23:59:59-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc>            <textClass>
